ampc (Asynchronous Music Player Controller) is an emacs application providing an interface to MPD ([http://mpd.wikia.com/]).  ampc can be installed via the GNU [[ELPA]].  The code of ampc can be found here: [http://ch.ristopher.com/git/?p=ampc;f=ampc.el;hb=master] (development version) or here: Lisp:ampc.el (stable version).  The development history can be found here: [http://ch.ristopher.com/git/?p=ampc;a=log].

